overview: Min-ah finds herself on a stranger's bed when she wakes up.  She's handcuffed.  Stranger Nam-gyu was next to her.  I want to let you go but my heart  wants you to stay...  I know it might be tough but stay here with me...  What's your name stranger?  Sorry  but I love you
tagline: I want to be with you even if it's for one night.  I can do that.  I think that's how I'll live.  Don't you remember who I am???
title: Keep [Breed - Her Inside Me]
